{
  "id": "weather-report",
  "name": "天气预报",
  "category": "weather",
  "description": "一份天气预报卡片，带有气象元素和天气图标",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.02,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "天气|气象|晴天|雨天|雪天|风暴",
        "description": "天气相关场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "location": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "地点"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日期"
    },
    "weather": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "晴",
      "options": ["晴", "多云", "阴", "雨", "雪", "风暴"],
      "description": "天气状况"
    },
    "temperature": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "温度"
    },
    "humidity": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "湿度"
    },
    "wind": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "风向风力"
    },
    "forecast": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 200,
      "description": "天气预报详情"
    },
    "suggestion": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "出行建议"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一份天气预报。\n\n背景信息：\n- 地点：{{location}}\n- 天气：{{weather}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用天气预报风格的语言\n2. 内容要包含温度、湿度等信息\n3. 可以包含出行建议\n4. 字数控制在100-200字之间\n\n请直接输出天气预报内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "weather",
    "colors": ["#3498db", "#87ceeb", "#f39c12"],
    "mood": "清新自然"
  },
  "rarity": "common",
  "collectible": true
}